# Cursor Rules for SreeharshaParuchuri1-v2.github.io
goal: Keep edits minimal and focused. Customize HTML/CSS and assets without rewriting everything.

read:
  - index.html
  - index_new.html
  - index_original.html
  - projects_section.html
  - quotes.html
  - create_simple_placeholders.html
  - stylesheet.css
  - images/**/*.{png,jpg,jpeg,svg,webp,avif}
  - data/**/*.{json,csv,txt}
  - README.md

write:
  - index.html
  - index_new.html
  - projects_section.html
  - quotes.html
  - stylesheet.css
  - images/*
  - resume.pdf
  - CNAME

hard_excludes:
  - .git/**
  - node_modules/**
  - **/*.{mp4,mov,mkv,avi,zip,tar,gz,7z,psd,ai}
  - **/*.py        # keep placeholder scripts untouched unless asked
  - **/__pycache__/**

notes:
  - Do not rewrite entire HTML files unless explicitly requested.
  - Keep design minimalist, professional, and accessible.
  - Prefer small, modular changes (e.g., update links, text, colors) over sweeping rewrites.
  - Preserve lightweight performance (optimize images, avoid heavy JS).
  - Maintain consistency with Jon Barronâ€™s clean aesthetic.
